---
import { markdownify } from "@/lib/utils/textConverter";
import CustomButton from "@/components/CustomButton.astro";
---

<section class="py-24 bg-white border-t-2 border-black">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 aspect-video flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-black relative group hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-shadow duration-300">
            {/* Simple CSS representation of the chart concept */}
            <div class="flex items-end gap-4 h-32 w-full max-w-xs z-10 border-b-2 border-black pb-2">
                <div class="w-16 bg-red-500 h-full relative border-2 border-black group-hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity">
                    <span class="absolute -top-6 left-0 text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase">Before</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-16 bg-[#00C853] h-[10%] relative border-2 border-black">
                    <span class="absolute -top-6 left-0 text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase">After</span>
                </div>
            </div>
             <p class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 text-[10px] text-black font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-wider bg-white px-1 border border-black">Real Client Data</p>
             <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[size:20px_20px] opacity-10" style="background-image: linear-gradient(#000 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, #000 1px, transparent 1px);"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none text-black">
            Featured Work: <br/><span class="text-black decoration-4 underline decoration-[#00C853] underline-offset-4">The 10,000-Page Pruning Project</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-black leading-relaxed font-mono">
          A US-based law firm was hit by a Google update, losing significant traffic. I audited their 10,000+ page site, identified 97% of it as thin or 'zombie' content, and executed a strategy to prune it down to ~300 high-value URLs.
        </p>
        <CustomButton label="Read Full Case Study" url="/portfolio" class="btn-primary !border-2 !border-black !rounded-none hover:shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-shadow" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
